songs.title: Tellin’ Me
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: Fifth Harmony]
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na

[Verse 1: Lauren (Dinah live)]
Pack your bags we're about to go
Further than you'll ever know
Close your eyes and just make a wish
I'll give you something you can't resist

[Pre-Chorus: Camila & All]
I wanna take you where you've never been, never been
I wanna take you where you've never been before
I wanna take you where you've never been, never been
I wanna take you where you've never been before

[Chorus: Fifth Harmony]
We're fallin' down, fallin' down, fallin' down to the floor
Keep tellin' me, tellin' me, tellin' me that I'm yours
I'm whatcha been, whatcha been, whatcha been waiting for
Keep tellin' me, tellin' me, tellin' me that I'm yours

[Post-Chorus]
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
(Keep tellin' me, tellin' me, tellin' me that I'm yours)
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na

[Verse 2: Normani & Camila]
I'll take your hand and just breathe it in
Baby, you will feel it within
Don't be shy, baby, follow me
Trust me, boy, I'll be all you need (Oh ooh)

[Pre-Chorus: Camila & All]
I wanna take you where you've never been, never been
I wanna take you where you've never been before
I wanna take you where you've never been, never been
I wanna take you where you've never been before

[Chorus: Fifth Harmony]
We're fallin' down, fallin' down, fallin' down to the floor
Keep tellin' me, tellin' me, tellin' me that I'm yours
I'm whatcha been, whatcha been, whatcha been waiting for
Keep tellin' me, tellin' me, tellin' me that I'm yours

[Post-Chorus]
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
(Keep tellin' me, tellin' me, tellin' me that I'm yours)
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na

[Bridge: Lauren]
If you really want me, baby, let me know
If you really love me, baby, tell me so
If you really mean it, baby, let me know
If you really want me, let me take you where you've never been before

[Chorus:]
We're fallin' down, fallin' down, fallin' down to the floor
Keep tellin' me, tellin' me, tellin' me that I'm yours
I'm whatcha been, whatcha been, whatcha been waiting for
Keep tellin' me, tellin' me, tellin' me that I'm yours

[Post-Chorus]
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
(Keep tellin' me, tellin' me, tellin' me that I'm yours)
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
(Keep tellin' me, tellin' me, tellin' me that I'm yours)
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
(Keep tellin' me, tellin' me, tellin' me that I'm yours)
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na
Na-na-na-na-na-na-na

[Outro]
Keep tellin' me, tellin' me, tellin' me that I'm yours
